protobuf
--------
Download and install from http://code.google.com/p/protobuf/
$ brew install protobuf

scons
-----
$ brew install scons

OSXFuse
-------
$ brew install osxfuse
$ ln -s /usr/local/Cellar/osxfuse/2.7.6/include/osxfuse/fuse fuse
## NOTE: replace cellar dir above with your version of fuse.

iphonedisk
----------
$ scons


Packaging "Disk for iPhone"
---------------------------
The installer project "Disk for iPhone" in th pkg/ subdirectory can be built
with the Iceberg installer, available from:
  http://s.sudre.free.fr/Software/Iceberg.html
The installer project depends on MacFUSE.pkg being placed in the pkg/
subdirectory.
